a leader in implant dentistry -- -an excellent text for novice and experienced alike michael block is an extraordinary educator and this text demonstrates his teaching abilities and his knowledge of implant dentistry . he sits on the education committees of several scientific academies for a reason . there is content appropriate for all dentists , not just oral surgeons . the text is easy to navigate through , there are ample references that will be helpful to students and educators alike , and the images , etc . are helpful towards clarifying concepts in implant dentistry . it is a must for every advanced implant surgeon and cutting edge restorative clinician